{"tid":535092,"cid":21,"subCid":4,"title":"一句講晒,宣美定請夏!","createTime":"2018-01-20T13:19:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-08T04:53:45.000Z","uid":56701,"like":51,"dislike":59,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"4b521b5cf0dda0efbe5c6ee02d55988fe9f2bb15","tid":535092,"uid":56701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T13:19:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gIsDpBMXbLo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DgIsDpBMXbLo&d=E75aot0gCfojnsAZZOEX89r9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=ce720d6b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gIsDpBMXbLo</a><br />\n<br />\n宣美呢個CB舞台幾正...夠晒SEX又有美感! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=No5vCemP1iQ&amp;t=26s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DNo5vCemP1iQ%26t%3D26s&d=E75aot0gCfojnsAZZOEX89r9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=806c3f33\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=No5vCemP1iQ&amp;t=26s</a><br />\n<br />\n請夏特登揀呢個舞台...好青春,好活力...好性感,正!<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n宣美=<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n請夏=<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n暫時覺得宣美今次太瘦,好冷艷咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔似之前首歌,瘦得嚟好健康又型!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n反而請夏成個舞台都好眼前一亮既感覺,好正!<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申:之前宣美首歌勁鐘意...去旅行都開住Youtube嚟聽!"},{"pid":"3325d3af4817508cea465cbbf9c291ae96c257aa","tid":535092,"uid":2313,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T14:26:33.000Z","msg":"Summi"},{"pid":"1a74205d5691b77eddf5097fa89259e2071169ae","tid":535092,"uid":118933,"like":18,"dislike"